org.afplib.afplib

Interface OBP

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OBPImpl

    public interface OBP
extends SF
    A representation of the model object 'OBP'.

    The following features are supported:

    • OA Pos ID
    • RG Length
    • Xoa Oset
    • Yoa Oset
    • Xoa Orent
    • Yoa Orent
    • Xoca Oset
    • Yoca Oset
    • Xoca Orent
    • Yoca Orent
    • Ref CSys

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getOBP()
